These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up
There 2 different types of food: radish, strawberry
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, board-games
The people have 2 different jobs:  engineer, accountant
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, country
2 different pets are kept: hamster, cat
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating strawberry##1
4. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
5. the accountant is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | 7up        |
| Food          | strawberry    | radish     |
| Hobby         | board-games | card-games   |
| Job           | engineer  | accountant |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | country       |
| Pet           | cat   | hamster      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: artichoke, onion
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, board-games
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, techno
There are 2 different nationalities: german, colombian
2 different pets are kept: rat, hedgehog
1. the colombian is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
2. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
3. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating onion is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Beverage      | fanta       | lemonade      |
| Food          | artichoke   | onion |
| Hobby         | skydiving | board-games  |
| Music-Genre   | techno        | soul     |
| Nationality   | german       | colombian   |
| Pet           | rat        | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, collecting
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, country
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, colombian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, handball
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
2. the colombian is on the left of the fan of country##1
3. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the fan of country is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |
| Beverage      | sprite      | lemonade   |
| Hobby         | sudoku | collecting |
| Music-Genre   | soul   | country    |
| Nationality   | colombian | indonesian  |
| Sport         | weightlifting      | handball  |
| Transport     | snowmobile    | helicopter     |

